📍 Problem: Reverse String

Question:
Write a function that reverses a string in-place using recursion.

Code:

class Solution {
    public void reverseString(char[] s) {
        swap(s, 0, s.length - 1);
    }

    public void swap(char[] s, int left, int right) {
        if (left >= right) {
            return;
        }
        char temp = s[left];
        s[left] = s[right];
        s[right] = temp;
        swap(s, left + 1, right - 1);
    }
}


Time Complexity: O(n)
Space Complexity: O(n) (recursion stack)
